=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 或者無意中係ig見到佢嘅蹤影</blockquote><br />\n冇follow佢新ig廢事眼冤呀<br />\n你unfollow佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日stalk佢好咩？"},{"pid":"df07ff26fbe7560c8bfe38d151815c878c88f23b","tid":214043,"uid":44446,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T15:50:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Block 左佢然後del埋佢，佢搵你唔到，你又搵唔到佢</blockquote><br />\n佢一早就block咗我wtsapp<br />\n用緊單機版wtsapp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係同佢嘅合照擺哂喺dropbox<br />\n點知搵緊野嗰陣唔小心click咗入去<br />\n結果 冇呀 又懷念以前嘅日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f0ff91dbcac109de3d73d57b93297a6c49b23ac","tid":214043,"uid":27793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T15:51:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇左做一人一個做低ex既 方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0b85d33310a81f8c50f42af8f01b241e34a831e","tid":214043,"uid":44446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T15:51:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>溝佢個好姊妹</blockquote><br />\n我同佢好兄弟好frd 唔會有發展空間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0116402aed734ae59ae58b56f4076e916cbf19e5","tid":214043,"uid":41009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T15:51:48.000Z","msg":"一諗起開心既回憶<br />\n就同時要自己諗佢唔好既野<br />\n諗返佢對自己有幾差<br />\n好自然就放得低"},{"pid":"2ab6c1c0cf478dd30435d3bb8b1d1ec3a1b8c420","tid":214043,"uid":44446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T15:51:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>移民</blockquote><br />\n哪有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p