c=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然仲好愛佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有 <br />\n一開始仲成日嗌交<br />\n但係我真係好鍾意<br />\n放唔低"},{"pid":"34c6b03199bdc9861e2851e084642025147dc02e","tid":214043,"uid":5937,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T16:44:09.000Z","msg":"聽講話重複做一樣嘢21日就可以培養成習慣<br />\n我嗰陣為咗忘記一個人<br />\n就逼自己每日唔去留意佢嘅所有嘢 忍21日<br />\n同埋培養幾樣習慣 等自己忘記咗培養呢堆習慣係為咗忘記佢<br />\nDone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f75438b9ce91c8e72d0ddcbd34b519bb55fe3aa8","tid":214043,"uid":93540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T16:57:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>時間係最重要 <br />\n搵新一個的確可以忘記前度 <br />\n但你絕對要愛宜家呢個</blockquote><br />\n識到先得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋未放低上一個<br />\n貿貿然開始新一段關係對現任有啲唔公平<br />\n無論你有幾愛現任都好<br />\n個心唔係淨係愛佢一個就有不忠嘅成份啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n男人一生點都會有個女仔係放唔低 過左幾耐都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d11f03ed90153e3241caa1b5e9bb44150a72ae2","tid":214043,"uid":37575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T17:00:19.000Z","msg":"真係時間，當初差唔多兩年，重要係因為識到而家哩個先可以"},{"pid":"6b43f1b578dbe71036101cb212107af7b6f17091","tid":214043,"uid":55505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T17:00:29.000Z","msg":"放唔低表示由鳩佢"},{"pid":"a58244dc16e4ba26440ff3ce01488f517d603875","tid":214043,"uid":41113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T17:23:27.000Z","msg":"每次以為自己好似放低左<br />\n都會突然發夢夢到佢<br />\n然後又會掛住掛住<br />\n有時夜晚失眠諗起佢<br />\n又會諗到原來已經返唔到去好似以前咁<br />\n就算連同佢講下野都講唔到<br />\n個心又會開始痛<br />\n真係好難受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee3988af1cbacefc090c7397cf92e9e4550e48c3","tid":214043,"uid":9594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T17:35:09.000Z","msg":"中出佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d2240f4842d75ef1bca9806f1d5ed1695ca48e4","tid":214043,"uid":87229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T18:37:00.000Z","msg":"識着player 好短暫但留下一堆美好就突然消失 到呢架兩年都走唔出深淵<br />\n仲好記住佢 都好驚自己害下手"},{"pid":"50147ec95b4071d27b796d8bffae0f7b12179310","tid":214043,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T19:01:43.000Z","msg":"留名 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d47398076f93a2f4d3ab87e3fb4d228c1a861fe3","tid":214043,"uid":110622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T19:03:09.000Z","msg":"愈想忘記 愈難忘記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c6abb3414357c4fc38b1331d0cf83363e83a73e","tid":214043,"uid":110657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T19:27:48.000Z","msg":"過返以前無佢既生活搵返以前既節奏 慢慢就會變返以前既習慣 唔會再諗"},{"pid":"1fc373bad96f228a8be98c015c59b8c3b00761eb","tid":214043,"uid":93348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T19:34:28.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e395fb7a01797da84f1be07b342d47224d436cf1","tid":214043,"uid":44446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T22:18:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>無用架<br />\n我同第二個一齊又試過<br />\n做運動又試過<br />\n但兩年幾都放唔低<br />\n直至搵返佢一齊返</blockquote><br />\n復合唔會有條刺咩？<br />\n我同佢就唔得啦 <br />\n一諗起佢有幾狠心扔低我就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然仲好愛佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有 <br />\n一開始仲成日嗌交<br />\n但係我真係好鍾意<br />\n放唔低</blockquote><br />\n硬係覺得一鬧交就會攞返分手件事黎講<br />\n就真係冇意慾一齊返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc722225849256340632522b3cd4698b85377e34","tid":214043,"uid":44446,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T22:20:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽講話重複做一樣嘢21日就可以培養成習慣<br />\n我嗰陣為咗忘記一個人<br />\n就逼自己每日唔去留意佢嘅所有嘢 忍21日<br />\n同埋培養幾樣習慣 等自己忘記咗培養呢堆習慣係為咗忘記佢<br />\nDone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔止21日唔去留意佢<br />\n但之後搵一搵野 見到關於同佢嘅回憶<br />\n眼淚blabla流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9df6d1228973a4d5651898eb73c7878be3375a9a","tid":214043,"uid":44446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T22:21:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>時間係最重要 <br />\n搵新一個的確可以忘記前度 <br />\n但你絕對要愛宜家呢個</blockquote><br />\n識到先得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋未放低上一個<br />\n貿貿然開始新一段關係對現任有啲唔公平<br />\n無論你有幾愛現任都好<br />\n個心唔係淨係愛佢一個就有不忠嘅成份啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n男人一生點都會有個女仔係放唔低 過左幾耐都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可惜佢放唔低嘅人唔係我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae34e0c700d016aac68db9524d5bd7d03249d232","tid":214043,"uid":44446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T22:22:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係時間，當初差唔多兩年，重要係因為識到而家哩個先可以</blockquote><br />\n遇到一個肯接受你過去嘅人唔易嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n被分手 戴過帽點都有啲陰影"},{"pid":"823835742b663f2f403cafd712fdbca17d033c97","tid":214043,"uid":44446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T22:24:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>放唔低表示由鳩佢</blockquote><br />\n個心長期拿住拿住 好似穿咗個窿咁好咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b88daca845a19a3cb5cc9888c45e0fdfe1ad3ad","tid":214043,"uid":44446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T22:25:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每次以為自己好似放低左<br />\n都會突然發夢夢到佢<br />\n然後又會掛住掛住<br />\n有時夜晚失眠諗起佢<br />\n又會諗到原來已經返唔到去好似以前咁<br />\n就算連同佢講下野都講唔到<br />\n個心又會開始痛<br />\n真係好難受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n再可不可以回到輕吻嘴邊相約點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d94ed253fa6e0f48f5d5dee93c0f06ffcf92091e","tid":214043,"uid":44446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T22:27:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>過返以前無佢既生活搵返以前既節奏 慢慢就會變返以前既習慣 唔會再諗</blockquote><br />\n但過去快樂嘅回憶耐唔耐就出現返喺腦海<br />\n唔係我想記起佢掛住佢啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲要經常見面 叫我點放低佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0c73c3dc04a05a7d6bb47a696f71e2cac96a4f8","tid":214043,"uid":103229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T22:44:12.000Z","msg":"學習愛自己"},{"pid":"da069f442e7f80ab71aa3a1ea45606884c3870fc","tid":214043,"uid":59414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T22:49:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2b1a8a03edb840c7cb8a76c4e67927b9d40bb81","tid":214043,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T23:05:58.000Z","msg":"第一步係掉鳩曬佢啲野先<br />\n第二樣係，你一諗起佢就落街跑步跑到自己好攰翻去訓<br />\n第三樣就係識新既男仔黎傾計，陪你打機<br />\n第四樣就係唔好逼自己唔諗佢，你逼自己果陣其實都係提醒緊自己有呢個人<br />\n第五樣就係一樣歪曲啲既野，香港有西就有本錢，你天生係女人就唔應該做到咁賤，只要你肯，大把兵仔埋黎，無必要為左一個咁既賤人咁唔開心，你可以選擇唔做娘娘，但係無必要做兵<br />\n第六樣就係去試一啲新既野，搵下啲新既興趣，聽到絲打你講鐘意打機應該唔太外向? 試下外向啲識多啲人啦"},{"pid":"38d32ca3bc18d0086df35ada92e3d32240f5bb4f","tid":214043,"uid":87892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T23:39:47.000Z","msg":"訓教"},{"pid":"736849eb086e3a7d8d34dc992abfdbba41308f26","tid":214043,"uid":91433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T02:19:31.000Z","msg":"心跳停頓"},{"pid":"fcdc7ecbe93752d4c4b6e2f2121b6861efc1b894","tid":214043,"uid":43264,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T02:31:25.000Z","msg":"個個十零廿歲都以為自己會忘記唔到自己個ex，其實只要有一段新感情既話，最多兩三年就唔會再執著於舊果段，就算話驚未放低唔敢開始新感情，如果你好人好姐有人鐘意自己既話，最多都係兩三年就會忍唔住接受左第二個，一邊內疚一邊同新果個拍拖，跟住一邊覺得依家果個好但係都仲係放唔低舊愛，一邊慢慢對個ex越來越無感覺。跟住慢慢發現自己當年所謂既放唔低，某程度上有少少只不過係沉迷响話比自己有幾痴情既自我麻醉心態啫。"},{"pid":"c1a4600ec0e08cfdc5e134e5f10b711aad613da7","tid":214043,"uid":93356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T02:35:33.000Z","msg":"部怒情就係忘記EX既最好方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只可惜未搵到新仔姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e2516640fcf41021b34dda6e4f88d3812440469","tid":214043,"uid":93881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T02:46:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真係時間，當初差唔多兩年，重要係因為識到而家哩個先可以</blockquote><br />\n時間先係最好既藥<br />\n時間係沖淡到一切<br />\n你愈係逼自己忘記就忘記唔到"},{"pid":"1583ae4ad333b039adfe72952965afefca29a104","tid":214043,"uid":43458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T03:09:23.000Z","msg":"好似放低唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：分左手七個月"},{"pid":"5957a87d1c670ae18704132bc3e4ca5df6480780","tid":214043,"uid":44446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T03:40:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同你一樣咁犯賤 但決定唔會再理佢<br />\n我諗咁樣斷絕來往會易啲放低？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cf9aca91b79b120c098999cff2e1d77d8c17a51","tid":214043,"uid":37575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T03:40:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>真係時間，當初差唔多兩年，重要係因為識到而家哩個先可以</blockquote><br />\n遇到一個肯接受你過去嘅人唔易嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n被分手 戴過帽點都有啲陰影</blockquote><br />\n每個人都有過去㗎啦 (當然睇吓你過去係點啦，假設你話你做過雞嘅又真係好難有男人可以接受到嘅)<br />\n我嗰時都戴咗半頂，但冇㗎，有新嘅人出現都要去信對方㗎"},{"pid":"f73ebf7b7d05fc3a7fec51590e153e677fd67534","tid":214043,"uid":44446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T03:43:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>第一步係掉鳩曬佢啲野先<br />\n第二樣係，你一諗起佢就落街跑步跑到自己好攰翻去訓<br />\n第三樣就係識新既男仔黎傾計，陪你打機<br />\n第四樣就係唔好逼自己唔諗佢，你逼自己果陣其實都係提醒緊自己有呢個人<br />\n第五樣就係一樣歪曲啲既野，香港有西就有本錢，你天生係女人就唔應該做到咁賤，只要你肯，大把兵仔埋黎，無必要為左一個咁既賤人咁唔開心，你可以選擇唔做娘娘，但係無必要做兵<br />\n第六樣就係去試一啲新既野，搵下啲新既興趣，聽到絲打你講鐘意打機應該唔太外向? 試下外向啲識多啲人啦</blockquote><br />\n第一步完全做唔到<br />\n一諗起佢以前咁花心機整禮物比我就唔捨得扔<br />\n淨係pack好放咗上櫃頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其他都有嘗試過 但去到某一日<br />\n回憶就突然標出黎咁<br />\n唔係我想去記住佢 係回憶唔比我忘記佢<br />\n仲要經常見面 佢有意無意喺我面前同其他異性close啲<br />\n屌佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60a55a215f4e614204ad9b1f3cb9ec47d8356a87","tid":214043,"uid":44446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T03:46:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個個十零廿歲都以為自己會忘記唔到自己個ex，其實只要有一段新感情既話，最多兩三年就唔會再執著於舊果段，就算話驚未放低唔敢開始新感情，如果你好人好姐有人鐘意自己既話，最多都係兩三年就會忍唔住接受左第二個，一邊內疚一邊同新果個拍拖，跟住一邊覺得依家果個好但係都仲係放唔低舊愛，一邊慢慢對個ex越來越無感覺。跟住慢慢發現自己當年所謂既放唔低，某程度上有少少只不過係沉迷响話比自己有幾痴情既自我麻醉心態啫。</blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打咁客觀去睇件事<br />\n或者過多幾年呢個人真係會慢慢從我嘅世界消失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ca691de8cd9c7767ca578626848406fb6f110cd","tid":214043,"uid":44446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T03:49:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>真係時間，當初差唔多兩年，重要係因為識到而家哩個先可以</blockquote><br />\n遇到一個肯接受你過去嘅人唔易嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n被分手 戴過帽點都有啲陰影</blockquote><br />\n每個人都有過去㗎啦 (當然睇吓你過去係點啦，假設你話你做過雞嘅又真係好難有男人可以接受到嘅)<br />\n我嗰時都戴咗半頂，但冇㗎，有新嘅人出現都要去信對方㗎</blockquote><br />\n一諗到以前喺街跪佢<br />\n佢發脾氣話我掛住溫書冇理佢<br />\n我就喺佢樓下淋雨等佢成晚<br />\n(結果佢掛住打機冇落過黎搵我)<br />\n比我咁好彩遇到下一個<br />\n都驚對方嫌棄我嘅過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f6b584899378c2b696f212368121a6351706284","tid":214043,"uid":89411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T03:49:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>個個十零廿歲都以為自己會忘記唔到自己個ex，其實只要有一段新感情既話，最多兩三年就唔會再執著於舊果段，就算話驚未放低唔敢開始新感情，如果你好人好姐有人鐘意自己既話，最多都係兩三年就會忍唔住接受左第二個，一邊內疚一邊同新果個拍拖，跟住一邊覺得依家果個好但係都仲係放唔低舊愛，一邊慢慢對個ex越來越無感覺。跟住慢慢發現自己當年所謂既放唔低，某程度上有少少只不過係沉迷响話比自己有幾痴情既自我麻醉心態啫。</blockquote><br />\n多謝巴打咁客觀去睇件事<br />\n或者過多幾年呢個人真係會慢慢從我嘅世界消失<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢個真 個時同初戀散 同fd講呢世唔拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"657cbeefce0abd2b68eb8a4688d7bdfd73ebeafd","tid":214043,"uid":37575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T03:56:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>真係時間，當初差唔多兩年，重要係因為識到而家哩個先可以</blockquote><br />\n遇到一個肯接受你過去嘅人唔易嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n被分手 戴過帽點都有啲陰影</blockquote><br />\n每個人都有過去㗎啦 (當然睇吓你過去係點啦，假設你話你做過雞嘅又真係好難有男人可以接受到嘅)<br />\n我嗰時都戴咗半頂，但冇㗎，有新嘅人出現都要去信對方㗎</blockquote><br />\n一諗到以前喺街跪佢<br />\n佢發脾氣話我掛住溫書冇理佢<br />\n我就喺佢樓下淋雨等佢成晚<br />\n(結果佢掛住打機冇落過黎搵我)<br />\n比我咁好彩遇到下一個<br />\n都驚對方嫌棄我嘅過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁唔係啲咩過去嚟啫，只係表示你當時好全心全意投入當時段感情，有啲失去自我啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1eba7528a0269d65980c793988da5fb5b7de5ac","tid":214043,"uid":43264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T04:40:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>真係時間，當初差唔多兩年，重要係因為識到而家哩個先可以</blockquote><br />\n遇到一個肯接受你過去嘅人唔易嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n被分手 戴過帽點都有啲陰影</blockquote><br />\n每個人都有過去㗎啦 (當然睇吓你過去係點啦，假設你話你做過雞嘅又真係好難有男人可以接受到嘅)<br />\n我嗰時都戴咗半頂，但冇㗎，有新嘅人出現都要去信對方㗎</blockquote><br />\n一諗到以前喺街跪佢<br />\n佢發脾氣話我掛住溫書冇理佢<br />\n我就喺佢樓下淋雨等佢成晚<br />\n(結果佢掛住打機冇落過黎搵我)<br />\n比我咁好彩遇到下一個<br />\n都驚對方嫌棄我嘅過去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n邊個無on9過丫，話無果個只係因為佢依家仲係on9緊"},{"pid":"92c797e1ba838b5116ed3430516f20c5a8658c75","tid":214043,"uid":15409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T04:46:03.000Z","msg":"夜蒲"},{"pid":"9da8a0e0685890338768adfaae6c3ac57437169a","tid":214043,"uid":86275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T04:48:57.000Z","msg":"佢係一隻雞 唔可以沉船<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就係咁樣"},{"pid":"f65c4504ebdd7489611d1a5c978ef955bd3357a3","tid":214043,"uid":41009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T04:55:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一諗起開心既回憶<br />\n就同時要自己諗佢唔好既野<br />\n諗返佢對自己有幾差<br />\n好自然就放得低</blockquote><br />\n我就係賤到無論佢對我有幾衰<br />\n只要記起佢一樣好嘅野<br />\n就原諒到佢差嘅一面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能我同ex之間唔好既回憶多過開心回憶啦<br />\n就算日日都戴住佢送既錶<br />\n都好清楚已經唔會再返轉頭<br />\n特登cap低晒臨分手果排d pk wtsapp<br />\n等諗起佢果陣用黎同自己講 值得心痛咩？"},{"pid":"d0f431c5ac748e6ea772b2928eeaea8c8ab79d4b","tid":214043,"uid":47548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T04:59:13.000Z","msg":"我唔主張逃避<br />\n試過唔得亦無悔 <br />\n<br />\n幫過4個巴打 都有2個復合成功 <br />\n信我既 留下tg 為了愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：復合失敗者"},{"pid":"a8ba069f481c57e5bbedd6a3a306c7661e6c565b","tid":214043,"uid":97526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T05:10:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我唔主張逃避<br />\n試過唔得亦無悔 <br />\n<br />\n幫過4個巴打 都有2個復合成功 <br />\n信我既 留下tg 為了愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：復合失敗者</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90a3ee49888870a361d335e0b39bfda9b9facd65","tid":214043,"uid":105934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T05:15:59.000Z","msg":"避開佢 包括所有同佢friend既人<br />\n不過同時亦會更掛住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5180bf98b8769fb9d945459dcbee1180cd7b1fc","tid":214043,"uid":89331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T05:25:04.000Z","msg":"唔識個新既都幾難忘記 但係睇住同新仔一齊個心又好似死死地"},{"pid":"43bc4b1184cc0bc80de7b669ecf038250e8fbc3e","tid":214043,"uid":91961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T14:18:52.000Z","msg":"我唔想放低我想佢返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e92310a8b8d0a84781be6c6ea82600942e71788","tid":214043,"uid":74407,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T14:45:01.000Z","msg":"一係咁啦 你去搵佢復合 煩住佢 等佢blacklist你 你知冇機會就會死心架喇"},{"pid":"b87038183d58e78ca76471ff2bc9229e04ae4203","tid":214043,"uid":103719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T16:54:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一係咁啦 你去搵佢復合 煩住佢 等佢blacklist你 你知冇機會就會死心架喇</blockquote><br />\n係幾好既諗法<br />\n利申已被block"},{"pid":"f6a51d4abde71ebf1788633eb43897ce230e62cd","tid":214043,"uid":109892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T17:06:22.000Z","msg":"Block無咩用 <br />\n最近用緊新方法 改對方個名<br />\n令到你一見到個名就打消搵返佢既念頭<br />\n例如 <br />\n有女朋友的前度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"866749835f0c680144d3eb9b50b201a3fa8ca31b","tid":214043,"uid":84015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T17:19:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>聽講話重複做一樣嘢21日就可以培養成習慣<br />\n我嗰陣為咗忘記一個人<br />\n就逼自己每日唔去留意佢嘅所有嘢 忍21日<br />\n同埋培養幾樣習慣 等自己忘記咗培養呢堆習慣係為咗忘記佢<br />\nDone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當初都想用呢個Theory氹自己放下同忘記<br />\n最後養成咗個習慣<br />\n係每日諗自己究竟放低佢未<br />\n其實姐係每日都諗起佢"},{"pid":"a4207874f6857be88c191874ab7a9329740a0e68","tid":214043,"uid":44446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T18:13:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>一諗起開心既回憶<br />\n就同時要自己諗佢唔好既野<br />\n諗返佢對自己有幾差<br />\n好自然就放得低</blockquote><br />\n我就係賤到無論佢對我有幾衰<br />\n只要記起佢一樣好嘅野<br />\n就原諒到佢差嘅一面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可能我同ex之間唔好既回憶多過開心回憶啦<br />\n就算日日都戴住佢送既錶<br />\n都好清楚已經唔會再返轉頭<br />\n特登cap低晒臨分手果排d pk wtsapp<br />\n等諗起佢果陣用黎同自己講 值得心痛咩？</blockquote><br />\n我仲用住佢送嘅袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明明佢做嘅野真係好仆街<br />\n但仍然停不了去掛住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d79ff0f6e1306ac7ece2dcd2dbf34e0f6f94692","tid":214043,"uid":44446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T18:15:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>避開佢 包括所有同佢friend既人<br />\n不過同時亦會更掛住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢好兄弟同我好frd(拍拖前已經熟)<br />\n冇奶由因為佢而同個frd斷絕來往架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63bf7667cb639d92c28b3d446b4f1edd1bf9cad5","tid":214043,"uid":44446,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T18:16:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我唔想放低我想佢返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同你相反<br />\n明知佢返黎大家個心都會有條刺<br />\n不如盡早學習放低啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f9b45ee3841bef8a6a5e2eb2a1d53a5af509f5e","tid":214043,"uid":44446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T18:17:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一係咁啦 你去搵佢復合 煩住佢 等佢blacklist你 你知冇機會就會死心架喇</blockquote><br />\n比佢block咗好撚耐<br />\n知道冇機會但諗起以前佢對我嘅好就掛住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8591e1026e8b3a741d48bdd8f8f50e2765eee066","tid":214043,"uid":44446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T18:18:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Block無咩用 <br />\n最近用緊新方法 改對方個名<br />\n令到你一見到個名就打消搵返佢既念頭<br />\n例如 <br />\n有女朋友的前度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n比佢block埋 save佢咩名都冇咩分別<br />\n大家有好多common groups<br />\n每次講完野都好留意佢有冇睇我個msg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49f18a7f7d6593969b368d2e35928601bec59b6a","tid":214043,"uid":44446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T18:19:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>聽講話重複做一樣嘢21日就可以培養成習慣<br />\n我嗰陣為咗忘記一個人<br />\n就逼自己每日唔去留意佢嘅所有嘢 忍21日<br />\n同埋培養幾樣習慣 等自己忘記咗培養呢堆習慣係為咗忘記佢<br />\nDone<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當初都想用呢個Theory氹自己放下同忘記<br />\n最後養成咗個習慣<br />\n係每日諗自己究竟放低佢未<br />\n其實姐係每日都諗起佢</blockquote><br />\n考試嗰排一忙就會慢慢唔記得呢個人<br />\n但依家考完做緊全職廢青<br />\n得閒冇野做又諗起佢又手多多去睇以前啲合照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7adc0183205cdf39e4378846ccd59b24085edfee","tid":214043,"uid":100184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T18:22:25.000Z","msg":"時間"},{"pid":"60e3319588abffcf76d34678955e31123a0309bc","tid":214043,"uid":109817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T18:39:36.000Z","msg":"留名學野 <br />\n<br />\n利申 今日比男朋友飛咗"},{"pid":"240ef5df41d8f8eecd51aceed43f805162ea27f0","tid":214043,"uid":13808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T18:41:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55e3e2acde5fbdd97164a9375f6f9d8a4ddf471f","tid":214043,"uid":109892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T18:51:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Block無咩用 <br />\n最近用緊新方法 改對方個名<br />\n令到你一見到個名就打消搵返佢既念頭<br />\n例如 <br />\n有女朋友的前度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n比佢block埋 save佢咩名都冇咩分別<br />\n大家有好多common groups<br />\n每次講完野都好留意佢有冇睇我個msg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大家個case唔同<br />\n起碼佢block你都算有啲良知<br />\n我嗰個已經有女朋友仲叫我出嚟飲嘢<br />\n咁先最仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔改返個名提自己驚唔夠定力做錯事"},{"pid":"72a4a4eb4bab8b9fe8485dc4c257e9a77d57d053","tid":214043,"uid":13569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T20:43:24.000Z","msg":"比佢傷害多一次就會瞓醒左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 未放抵佢既只不過係回憶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 比佢再傷就會記得傷害 慢慢就會淡忘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：只係我先用到咁樣效果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d361bce8f6e342311832f1ee3d7a66ec9370195","tid":214043,"uid":29947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T05:23:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我用左一年半時間都未放得低EX，主要原因係佢死都唔肯講清楚已經唔鍾意我，點知天網恢恢，俾我發現佢只係一條想收我做兵既大話精。<br />\n<br />\n而家當我有啲懷念過去時，都會<span style=\"color: red;\">即刻諗返佢有幾仆街同虛偽</span>，我諗我終於可以放低佢喇！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好方法！學下"},{"pid":"20d0c3ef49caf88546e8b13789f95126cf3fdc60","tid":214043,"uid":48267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T05:27:00.000Z","msg":"當你再得唔到，只可以唔好忘記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bb1052fd0b07ef216edfa39b7b87a2c061214de","tid":214043,"uid":59065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T05:38:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0caf068ed5c2fae521ab70ee74bbe5005ab0d24b","tid":214043,"uid":98805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T05:55:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>一係咁啦 你去搵佢復合 煩住佢 等佢blacklist你 你知冇機會就會死心架喇</blockquote><br />\n係幾好既諗法<br />\n利申已被block</blockquote><br />\n近排試過<br />\nblock咗真係會覺得好啲<br />\n起碼你會覺得佢係一個咁絕情嘅人，你對佢嘅留戀會再少啲<br />\n利申 ex散咗就話中意咗其他人（四年感情）"},{"pid":"0f79f7a7788cbf2579f60ea52aa924c335941638","tid":214043,"uid":75210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T05:57:40.000Z","msg":"有新目標/識到另一個就最快"},{"pid":"38b086062bbd4765af570532d830180dc21cce33","tid":214043,"uid":70566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T06:10:10.000Z","msg":"我好想自己可以死心"},{"pid":"446e785b7b044d3fdbf16e05815826a1badb8f7a","tid":214043,"uid":97104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T06:16:38.000Z","msg":"一無聊打開ex d J圖就放低唔到"},{"pid":"c014d2efa968a05e761ea00823616d59f651e728","tid":214043,"uid":84015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T06:22:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>當你再得唔到，只可以唔好忘記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果恨你 就能不忘記你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a201875b405727cf7ff1a7233c826d69796be02","tid":214043,"uid":89353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T14:34:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>無用架<br />\n我同第二個一齊又試過<br />\n做運動又試過<br />\n但兩年幾都放唔低<br />\n直至搵返佢一齊返</blockquote><br />\n復合唔會有條刺咩？<br />\n我同佢就唔得啦 <br />\n一諗起佢有幾狠心扔低我就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然仲好愛佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有 <br />\n一開始仲成日嗌交<br />\n但係我真係好鍾意<br />\n放唔低</blockquote><br />\n硬係覺得一鬧交就會攞返分手件事黎講<br />\n就真係冇意慾一齊返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n但係我係🤦🏼&zwj;♂️"},{"pid":"241cc9f9157c90e9aa2c527d136cb744ebc4ed9a","tid":214043,"uid":103719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T15:35:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>當你再得唔到，只可以唔好忘記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果恨你 就能不忘記你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好想憎你 咁我就唔洗再留戀"},{"pid":"77d6435de9b6a6d14f75e5c77c3873984b329621","tid":214043,"uid":561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T15:40:02.000Z","msg":"我決定周圍食女 但係當某一晚無女陪 就會諗起"}]}